<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Not a PDF</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>This file is HTML content saved under a .pdf name.</h1>
    <p>
      The E2E suite uploads it to Drive with the application/pdf MIME type so
      that Vision asyncBatchAnnotateFiles rejects it with INVALID_ARGUMENT,
      exercising the permanent-failure (single ACK, no retry) path of
      text-vision-processor.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
